    "BitKeeper was created by Larry McVoy in 1998.",
    "BitKeeper managed the Linux kernel source from 2002 to 2005.",
    "Andrew Tridgell reverse-engineered the BitKeeper protocol in 2005.",
    "Linus Torvalds began writing Git in April 2005.",
    "Git uses SHA-1 content addressing for data integrity.",
    "Junio Hamano took over as Git maintainer in July 2005.",
    "Matt Mackall released Mercurial in April 2005.",
    "GitHub was launched in 2008 by Tom Preston-Werner, Chris Wanstrath, PJ Hyett, and Scott Chacon."
  ]

